    "Comment": {
      "expanded": true,
      "value": "Convert TEI XML format to USFM\r\n\r\nDesigned for processing each of the books in VulgateGlaire\r\n\r\nDownloaded from https:\/\/github.com\/MarjorieBurghart\/VulgateGlaire\r\n\r\nHer text was obtained from http:\/\/jesusmarie.free.fr\/bible_vigouroux.html\r\n\r\nAssumes: subst V: <download_path>\r\n\r\nAnalysis:\r\n - Character frequency analysis on merged.usfm\r\n\r\nErratum: (+ reported upstream)\r\n - Remove space before a comma\r\n\r\nDone separately:\r\n + Rename each file with a 2 digit prefix & USFM book ID\r\n + Add markers: \\id \\ide \\rem \\h \\toc1 \\toc2 \\toc3 \\mt1 \\mt2\r\n \r\nTBD: (Were these done later?)\r\n + Use footnote markers for parenthesised notes\r\n + Use \\d and \\qa where applicable instead of \\it_...\\it*\r\n + Mark the 22 acrostic Hebrew letter names in Psalm 118.\r\n + Locate and fix the 9 unpaired parentheses \r\n + 20 instances of \\x{2019}\\x20 [remove the space]\r\n   Only where the next letter is a vowel.\r\n\r\n",
      "SubFilters": {
        "Comment": {
          "value": "Revision History:\r\n\r\n2017-10-10 Filter developed and used successfully\r\n2021-01-18 Filter saved in new JSON readable text format"
        },
        "Comment": {
          "value": "Tidy 1",
          "SubFilters": {
            "EOL": {
              "convertFrom": 3,
              "convertTo": 2,
              "fixedLineLength": 80,
              "removeExtraneous": false,
              "convertToText": ""
            },
            "Simple": {
              "filterType": 10
            },
            "Simple": {
              "filterType": 12
            }
          }
        },
        "Comment": {
          "value": "Convert",
          "SubFilters": {
            "Comment": {
              "expanded": true,
              "value": "ID",
              "SubFilters": {
                "Search": {
                  "search": "<div xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.tei-c.org\/ns\/1.0\" type=\"book\" xml:",
                  "replace": "",
                  "ignoreCase": false,
                  "patternType": 0,
                  "greedy": false,
                  "dotMatchesNewLines": true,
                  "utf8support": true
                }
              }
            },
            "Comment": {
              "expanded": true,
              "value": "Verses",
              "SubFilters": {
                "Search": {
                  "expanded": true,
                  "search": "<ab .+<\/ab>",
                  "replace": "",
                  "ignoreCase": false,
                  "patternType": 1,
                  "replaceType": 2,
                  "greedy": false,
                  "dotMatchesNewLines": true,
                  "utf8support": true,
                  "SubFilters": {
                    "SearchList": {
                      "useFile": false,
                      "simultaneous": false,
                      "onlyLogOnReplace": true,
                      "ignoreCase": false,
                      "patternType": 1,
                      "greedy": false,
                      "dotMatchesNewLines": true,
                      "utf8support": true,
                      "items": [
                        ["\\r\\n", "\\x20"],
                        ["<ab n=\"", "\\\\v\\x20"],
                        ["<\/ab>", ""]
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "Comment": {
              "expanded": true,
              "value": "Other",
              "SubFilters": {
                "SearchList": {
                  "useFile": false,
                  "simultaneous": false,
                  "ignoreCase": false,
                  "patternType": 1,
                  "greedy": false,
                  "dotMatchesNewLines": true,
                  "utf8support": true,
                  "items": [
                    ["id=\"", "\\\\id\\x20"],
                    ["<div type=\"chapter\" n=\"", "\\\\c\\x20"],
                    ["<\/div>", ""],
                    ["(<\/hi>)(\\.)", "$2$$1"],
                    ["<hi rend=\"italics\">(.+)<\/hi>", "\\\\it $1\\\\it*"],
                    ["\">", "\\x20"],
                    ["&#160;", "\\xC2\\xA0"]
                  ]
                },
                "Grep": {
                  "expanded": true,
                  "filterType": 0,
                  "value": "^\\\\id",
                  "ignoreCase": false,
                  "patternType": 0,
                  "utf8support": true,
                  "ignoreEmpty": false,
                  "SubFilters": {
                    "SearchList": {
                      "useFile": false,
                      "simultaneous": false,
                      "onlyLogOnReplace": true,
                      "ignoreCase": false,
                      "patternType": 1,
                      "greedy": true,
                      "dotMatchesNewLines": false,
                      "utf8support": true,
                      "items": [
                        ["(\\w+)_(\\w+)", "$2_$1"]
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "Comment": {
              "expanded": true,
              "value": "Fixes\r\n\r\nTBD: Remove space after ) where next letter is a vowel",
              "SubFilters": {
                "SearchList": {
                  "useFile": false,
                  "simultaneous": false,
                  "ignoreCase": false,
                  "patternType": 1,
                  "greedy": false,
                  "dotMatchesNewLines": true,
                  "utf8support": true
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "Comment": {
          "value": "Tidy 2",
          "SubFilters": {
            "Simple": {
              "filterType": 11
            },
            "Simple": {
              "filterType": 19
            }
          }
        },
        "Comment": {
          "value": "Acrostics\r\n\r\nMove the 22 acrostics in Ps 118 to before the verse & mark with \\qa \r\n& removed the redundant space and colon.\r\n\r\nReplace the italics markers in Lamentations by \\qac_...\\qac*\r\n\r\nNB. Has to be done after Tidy 2 else HETH is not matched.\r\n\r\nSWORD currently doesn't allocate a character style to the\r\ncorresponding OSIS defined <hi type=\"acrostic\">...<\/hi>\r\n\r\n",
          "SubFilters": {
            "String": {
              "expanded": true,
              "value": "^.+Ps.xml$",
              "matchCase": false,
              "filterType": 17,
              "SubFilters": {
